<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sustainability | Ylsoo</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="nav-content">
        <div class="nav-left">
          <a href="/" class="logo">Ylsoo</a>
          <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/journey">Journey</a>
            <a href="/trust">Trust</a>
            <a href="/sustainability" class="active">Sustainability</a>
            <a href="/partners">Partners</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-right">
          <% if (user) { %>
            <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-text">Dashboard</a>
            <button onclick="logout()" class="btn-primary">Sign out</button>
          <% } else { %>
            <a href="/login" class="btn-text">Sign in</a>
            <a href="/signup" class="btn-primary">Sign up</a>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Sustainability Page -->
  <section class="legal-document">
    <div class="legal-container">
      <div class="legal-header">
        <h1>Our Commitment to Sustainability</h1>
        <p class="legal-date">Updated November 2025</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>Driving Positive Change</h2>
          <p>
            At Ylsoo, we believe innovation should serve not only people but also the planet.  
            Our mission is to empower organizations to create technology that is energy-efficient, scalable, and responsible.  
            Every product and process at Ylsoo is designed to reduce waste, improve transparency, and maximize sustainability impact.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>Our Sustainability Principles</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Carbon Conscious:</strong> We actively reduce emissions by hosting on carbon-neutral data centers and optimizing compute workloads.</li>
            <li><strong>Responsible Innovation:</strong> Every line of code and feature is built with long-term impact in mind.</li>
            <li><strong>Circular Design:</strong> We emphasize longevity, modularity, and minimal digital waste in our systems.</li>
            <li><strong>Community Empowerment:</strong> We support tech education and green innovation across developing regions.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>Our Impact Goals</h2>
          <p>
            Ylsoo is committed to measurable action.  
            By 2030, we aim to achieve:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Net-zero operational carbon emissions.</li>
            <li>100% renewable-powered infrastructure.</li>
            <li>Full transparency in product lifecycle data.</li>
            <li>Reinvestment of 3% of annual profits into sustainability programs.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>Collaborating for a Greener Future</h2>
          <p>
            Sustainability is not a competition — it’s a collective mission.  
            Ylsoo works with international partners, startups, and non-profits to drive progress toward a cleaner, fairer digital economy.  
            We believe technology should lead the way toward a world that thrives on efficiency, equity, and shared innovation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-info">
          <strong>Contact Our Sustainability Team</strong>
          <p>
            Have a question or idea related to sustainability?  
            Reach out to our environmental innovation team directly:
            <br><a href="mailto:sustainability@ylsoo.com">sustainability@ylsoo.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-footer">
          <p>Learn more about how we build trust and transparency into everything we do.</p>
          <div class="legal-links">
            <a href="/trust">Trust Center</a>
            <span>|</span>
            <a href="/status">System Status</a>
            <span>|</span>
            <a href="/partners">Our Partners</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div class="footer-col">
          <h4>Products</h4>
          <a href="#">Ylsoo Cloud</a>
          <a href="#">Ylsoo Analytics</a>
          <a href="#">Ylsoo Workspace</a>
          <a href="#">Ylsoo Security</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-col">
          <h4>Resources</h4>
          <a href="#">Documentation</a>
          <a href="#">API Reference</a>
          <a href="#">Blog</a>
          <a href="#">Support</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-col">
          <h4>Legal</h4>
          <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>
          <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
          <a href="/cookies">Cookie Policy</a>
          <a href="/sustainability">Sustainability</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-col">
          <h4>Company</h4>
          <a href="/about">About Us</a>
          <a href="/partners">Partners</a>
          <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
          <a href="/trust">Trust Center</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Ylsoo. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    async function logout() {
      const res = await fetch('/api/logout', { method: 'POST' });
      const data = await res.json();
      if (data.success) window.location.href = data.redirect;
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
